title: Low Millions
text:
The Low Millions are a pop-rock band from California.


== Discography ==
Ex-Girlfriends (2004)


== Members ==
Adam Cohen – vocals, guitar(singer/guitarist)
Michael Chaves – vocals, guitar
Jorgen Carlsson – vocals, bass
Erik Eldenius – drums
